headline: TAPFIN Hits a Dozen: Everest Group Recognizes Transformative Workforce Leader for 12th Consecutive Year
summary: Talent Solutions TAPFIN, the managed service provider (MSP) arm of ManpowerGroup family of brands has been named a Global Leader in Everest Group's 2025 Contingent Workforce Management (CWM) PEAK Matrix® Assessment for an unprecedented 12th consecutive year. TAPFIN was also recognized as a Leader in Services Procurement (SOW) for the fourth straight year, further strengthening its role as a trusted strategic workforce partner for global organizations.
